title: An Interview with Kenny Wheeler, Composer and Jazz Trumpet Player
fulltitle: An Interview with Kenny Wheeler, Composer and Jazz Trumpet Player

http_headers.User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/75.0.3759.3 Safari/537.36

description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Kenny Wheeler talks about his life's experiences including his childhood, his father, and how he learned his craft. He discusses musicians who influenced him and some of the people with whom he's played.
